  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485310/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765008487\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485310/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765008487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485310/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765008487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Take a role in a caroonish styled FPS multiplayer game. Choose among 5 characters and bunch of weapons and play Head Shot online with friends and strangers.<br><br>Features:<br>-5 classes (Assault, Sniper, Engineer, Medic, Machine Gunner);<br>-Various types of weapons including  Assaults, Equipments, Machine Guns, Pistols, Rocket Launchers, Shotguns and Snipers;<br>-Vehicles;<br>-Different game modes (currently Death Match and Team Death Match)<br><br>Planned features:<br>-More weapons;<br>-More game modes;<br>-More items and various other content that will bring more fun into the game.<br>-Open chest system and various other stuff...<br><br><br>More features coming soon.",
  "about_the_game": "Take a role in a caroonish styled FPS multiplayer game. Choose among 5 characters and bunch of weapons and play Head Shot online with friends and strangers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n-5 classes (Assault, Sniper, Engineer, Medic, Machine Gunner);<br />\r\n-Various types of weapons including  Assaults, Equipments, Machine Guns, Pistols, Rocket Launchers, Shotguns and Snipers;<br />\r\n-Vehicles;<br />\r\n-Different game modes (currently Death Match and Team Death Match)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlanned features:<br />\r\n-More weapons;<br />\r\n-More game modes;<br />\r\n-More items and various other content that will bring more fun into the game.<br />\r\n-Open chest system and various other stuff...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore features coming soon.",
  "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Turkish, French, Italian, Polish<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
